this another series of NAGA ANTABOGA.
Antaboga is symbolize as a Guardian of underworld in Indonesia, especially in Java and Bali Island culture.
This is reinforced based on Wayang / traditional puppet story, ancient manuscripts such as the story of the book Udyogaparwa, Tantu Panggelaran, and Korawasrama.
